Sentencas: Electrolyte-free fuel cell (EFFC) which holds the similar function with the traditional solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) but possesses a completely different structure, has draw much attention during these years.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte-free fuel cell with Mg0.4Zn0.6O/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ-Li0.3Ni0.6Cu0.07Sr0.03O2-δ layer

Sentencas: Herein, we report a complex of MZSDC LNCS (Mg0.4Zn0.6O/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-delta-Li0.3Ni0.6Cu0.07Sr0.03O2-delta) for EFFC that demonstrates a high electrochemical power output of about 600 mW cm(-2) at 630 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte-free fuel cell with Mg0.4Zn0.6O/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ-Li0.3Ni0.6Cu0.07Sr0.03O2-δ layer

Sentencas: The co-doped MZSDC is synthesized by a co-precipitation method.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte-free fuel cell with Mg0.4Zn0.6O/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ-Li0.3Ni0.6Cu0.07Sr0.03O2-δ layer

Sentencas: Semiconductor material of LNCS is synthesized by direct solid state reaction.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte-free fuel cell with Mg0.4Zn0.6O/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ-Li0.3Ni0.6Cu0.07Sr0.03O2-δ layer

Sentencas: The microstructure and morphology of the composite materials are characterized by X-ray diffraction (XRD), scanning electron microscope (SEM) and energy-dispersive Xray spectrometer (EDS).
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte-free fuel cell with Mg0.4Zn0.6O/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ-Li0.3Ni0.6Cu0.07Sr0.03O2-δ layer

Sentencas: The performance of the cell with a large size (6 x 6 cm(2)) is comparable or even better than that of the conventional solid oxide fuel cells with large sizes.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte-free fuel cell with Mg0.4Zn0.6O/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ-Li0.3Ni0.6Cu0.07Sr0.03O2-δ layer

Sentencas: The maximum power output of 9.28 W is obtained from the large-size cell at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte-free fuel cell with Mg0.4Zn0.6O/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ-Li0.3Ni0.6Cu0.07Sr0.03O2-δ layer

Sentencas: This paper develops a new functional nanocomposite for EFFC which is conducive to its commercial use.
Titulo: Fabrication of electrolyte-free fuel cell with Mg0.4Zn0.6O/Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-δ-Li0.3Ni0.6Cu0.07Sr0.03O2-δ layer
